README.md
     1Ôćĺ# Versioning Library for Go
     2Ôćĺ
     3Ôćĺ![Build Status](https://github.com/hashicorp/go-version/actions/workflows/go-tests.yml/badge.svg)
     4Ôćĺ[![Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/badge/github.com/hashicorp/go-version.svg)](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-version)
     5Ôćĺ
     6Ôćĺgo-version is a library for parsing versions and version constraints,
     7Ôćĺand verifying versions against a set of constraints. go-version
     8Ôćĺcan sort a collection of versions properly, handles prerelease/beta
     9Ôćĺversions, can increment versions, etc.
    10Ôćĺ
    11ÔćĺVersions used with go-version must follow [SemVer](http://semver.org/).
    12Ôćĺ
    13Ôćĺ## Installation and Usage
    14Ôćĺ
    15ÔćĺPackage documentation can be found on
    16Ôćĺ[Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-version).
    17Ôćĺ
    18ÔćĺInstallation can be done with a normal `go get`:
    19Ôćĺ
    20Ôćĺ```
    21Ôćĺ$ go get github.com/hashicorp/go-version
    22Ôćĺ```
    23Ôćĺ
    24Ôćĺ#### Version Parsing and Comparison
    25Ôćĺ
    26Ôćĺ```go
    27Ôćĺv1, err := version.NewVersion("1.2")
    28Ôćĺv2, err := version.NewVersion("1.5+metadata")
    29Ôćĺ
    30Ôćĺ// Comparison example. There is also GreaterThan, Equal, and just
    31Ôćĺ// a simple Compare that returns an int allowing easy >=, <=, etc.
    32Ôćĺif v1.LessThan(v2) {
    33Ôćĺ    fmt.Printf("%s is less than %s", v1, v2)
    34Ôćĺ}
    35Ôćĺ```
    36Ôćĺ
    37Ôćĺ#### Version Constraints
    38Ôćĺ
    39Ôćĺ```go
    40Ôćĺv1, err := version.NewVersion("1.2")
    41Ôćĺ
    42Ôćĺ// Constraints example.
    43Ôćĺconstraints, err := version.NewConstraint(">= 1.0, < 1.4")
    44Ôćĺif constraints.Check(v1) {
    45Ôćĺ	fmt.Printf("%s satisfies constraints %s", v1, constraints)
    46Ôćĺ}
    47Ôćĺ```
    48Ôćĺ
    49Ôćĺ#### Version Sorting
    50Ôćĺ
    51Ôćĺ```go
    52ÔćĺversionsRaw := []string{"1.1", "0.7.1", "1.4-beta", "1.4", "2"}
    53Ôćĺversions := make([]*version.Version, len(versionsRaw))
    54Ôćĺfor i, raw := range versionsRaw {
    55Ôćĺ    v, _ := version.NewVersion(raw)
    56Ôćĺ    versions[i] = v
    57Ôćĺ}
    58Ôćĺ
    59Ôćĺ// After this, the versions are properly sorted
    60Ôćĺsort.Sort(version.Collection(versions))
    61Ôćĺ```
    62Ôćĺ
    63Ôćĺ## Issues and Contributing
    64Ôćĺ
    65ÔćĺIf you find an issue with this library, please report an issue. If you'd
    66Ôćĺlike, we welcome any contributions. Fork this library and submit a pull
    67Ôćĺrequest.
